This document contains the user guide for the Yellow Duck Framework version 2.0.

The Yellow Duck Framework is an object oriented framework written in PHP which makes it a lot easier and faster to create websites and web applications.

The Yellow Duck Framework is proudly sponsered by Red Carpet Host.


                
                    
                
                
                    
                
            
        
    

